3. Database Models (Naye Tables Kya Banenge?)
WhatsApp features ko track karne ke liye humein 2 naye models banane honge:

A. WhatsAppOTP Model (in accounts/models.py)
OTP tracking aur validation ke liye.

phone_number (CharField)
otp (CharField - 4 or 6 digits)
created_at (DateTimeField)
expires_at (DateTimeField - current time + 5 minutes)
is_used (BooleanField - taaki ek OTP 2 baar use na ho)
B. WhatsAppLog Model (in appointment/models.py or new notifications app)
Future tracking aur debugging ke liye ki message gaya ya fail hua.

patient (ForeignKey to Patient)
phone_number (CharField)
template_name (CharField - e.g., 'booking_confirm')
status (CharField - 'Sent', 'Failed', 'Delivered')
response_data (JSONField - WhatsApp API ka response)
sent_at (DateTimeField)
4. Patient OTP Login Flow (Step-by-Step Changes)
Files to modify: accounts/views.py, accounts/urls.py, templates/accounts/login.html

Step 1 View (Send OTP): User apna phone number dalega. View me number aayega, random OTP generate hoga, WhatsAppOTP table me save hoga, aur Meta API ko call jayegi us number par OTP template bhejane ke liye.
Step 2 View (Verify OTP): User ko ek nayi screen/modal dikhegi OTP input karne ke liye. User OTP dalega, backend check karega WhatsAppOTP table me ki OTP correct hai aur expire toh nahi hua.
Authentication: Agar OTP correct hai, toh Custom Backend trigger hoga aur login(request, user) call hoga. Patient sidha dashboard par redirect ho jayega.
5. WhatsApp Message Automation (Kahan aur Kaise?)
Utility File: Hum ek alag file banayenge utils/whatsapp.py jisme API request bhejne ka generic code hoga send_whatsapp_template(phone, template_name, parameters).

Event 1: Appointment Booking
File: appointment/views.py (Class: Book_appointment & Add_appointment)
Hook: Jaise hi Appointment.objects.create(...) success hota hai, hum background me ya turant send_whatsapp_template call karenge patient ke phone number par.
Event 2: Prescription Generation
File: appointment/views.py (Class: PrescriptionView.post)
Hook: Jab doctor visit complete karta hai (is_completing = True) aur bill ban jata hai, tab hum prescription download link ya details generate karke patient ko message bhejenge.
Event 3: Appointment Cancellation
File: appointment/views.py (Function: cancel_appointment)
Hook: Status 'cancelled' me update hote hi notification send hoga "Aapki appointment cancel kar di gayi hai."
